#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#. +> trunk6
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "&chessament; is a chess tournament manager. It supports individual Swiss-system tournaments."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#. +> trunk6
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main features of &chessament;:"
msgstr ""

